assignBackupablesMap.description:
Key should be set to the current owner uuid, and values should be set to uuid of VMs/Shares that are in that owner. {
    "assignBackupablesMap":{ 
        "owner1Uuid":["vm1Uuid, ..."],
        "owner2Uuid":["share1Uuid, ..."]

    },
    "keepOriginalData" : false
}
